data.meta_description: UNITED STATES NAVY - KOREA  Marvin Allen Keen, Sr., age 76, 155 Pinnacle Drive, Elizabethtown, Tennessee, went home to be with the Lord Thursday, January 1, 2009 from the James A. Quillen VA Medical Center.  He was a native of Halltown, NJ and a son of the late Maurice and Reba Robinson Keen.  Mr. Keen was a member of...
